    "title": "Murf AI: Tips & Best Ways for Studio-Quality Voiceovers",
    "excerpt": "Discover how Murf AI delivers studio-grade voiceovers with 200+ voices. Learn best practices, standout features, and tips to create pro audio fast.",
    "featured_image": {
