        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I have recorded voiceovers in closets, under blankets, and once in a parked car to avoid background noise. If you have been there too, you know the pain: retake after retake, editing out breaths, and still ending up with audio that sounds amateur. Murf AI ended that cycle for me.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "After months of using it across client videos, internal presentations, and podcast intros, I can say this tool genuinely produces studio-quality output without the studio. Below I am sharing the tips, best practices, and specific workflows that helped me get the most out of it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://get.murf.ai/e5a3jr17jump"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start generating voiceovers for free with Murf AI",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — no credit card required.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why Murf AI Changed How I Produce Audio",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Before Murf, my audio workflow looked like this: script, record, re-record, edit, export, repeat. It ate hours. Murf AI compresses that entire chain into a single session inside a browser tab.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-murf-ai"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The core offering is a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "text-to-speech engine",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " powered by deep learning models trained on professional voice talent. You type or paste your script, pick a voice, adjust pacing and emphasis, and export. The result sounds like a human narrator who rehearsed for an hour — except it took you ninety seconds.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What impressed me first was the emotional range. Early TTS tools gave you robotic monotone. Murf's voices laugh, whisper, pause for effect, and shift tone mid-sentence. When I generated a demo for a client's explainer video, they asked which studio I hired. That is the level we are working with.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
