      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Test at least three voices per project. Murf's preview is instant, so this takes two minutes and dramatically improves the final result.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. Layer Audio with Video Inside Murf Studio",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l6",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-descript"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You do not need a separate video editor for simple projects. Murf Studio lets you sync voiceover with stock footage, images, and text overlays directly. I produced a 90-second social media ad entirely inside the platform — script to export in twenty minutes. For more complex video work, you might also explore tools like ",
