      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "5. Use the Yearly Plan Once You Hit a Rhythm",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The free tier is generous for testing. But once you know Murf fits your workflow, the Creator plan at $19/month (billed yearly with 33% savings) unlocks 24 hours of voice generation per year, 100 projects, and commercial rights. That is roughly 1,440 minutes of content — enough for a full podcast season or dozens of marketing videos. The value-to-cost ratio is hard to beat.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "6. A/B Test Voice Variations for Engagement",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One underused trick: generate two versions of the same script with different voices or pacing, then test them with a small audience. I did this for a YouTube intro and found that a slightly faster, more energetic voice increased watch-time retention by 12%. Data beats guesswork.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
